The paper discusses a machine learning algorithm for training Restricted Boltzmann Machines (RBM), which is a popular model in the field of deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions using the algorithm on benchmark datasets, which suggests that it could be relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT).
